    "description": {
      "value": "<div><div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Prerequisites: 7th level; @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.LTWVJZ5zPPXKWnM8] spell or a warlock feature that curses</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>Your curse creates a temporary bond between you and your target. As a bonus action, you can magically teleport up to 30 feet to an unoccupied space you can see within 5 feet of the target cursed by your @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.LTWVJZ5zPPXKWnM8] spell or by a warlock feature of yours, such as Hexblade's Curse or Sign of Ill Omen. To teleport in this way, you must be able to see the cursed target.</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div></div>",
